{"tid":948841,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"討厭達哥用打機穩錢既入一入","createTime":"2018-12-20T11:05:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-20T23:10:33.000Z","uid":74702,"like":145,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"432e51c01c54e544a9042838d28f2b1a52ff1388","tid":948841,"uid":74702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T11:05:45.000Z","msg":"成日上連登 見d人又話達哥收錢打機好仆街<br />\n我當佢真係有收錢，咁又有咩問題？<br />\n<br />\n打個比喻 有d 音樂家 因為中意音樂而唔係為錢 而簡呢個職業，<br />\n咁人地開音樂會 收人錢  唔通你又會話佢玩音樂係有心既 就應該一蚊都唔收？<br />\n<br />\n其實中意個樣野 ，又可以做到職業  又養活到自己有咩問題？<br />\n呢個市場好公平  佢靠到打機穩錢  證明佢係個市場有價值<br />\n<br />\n你地可以吊9佢d直播悶同垃圾  ，<br />\n但吊9佢 打機收錢真係好反智<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2718a3fba89e499857990670d2d02a12b6fb5c47","tid":948841,"uid":177089,"like":39,"dislike":3,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T11:08:38.000Z","msg":"香港人癲㗎"},{"pid":"a1ad315b47748ac8419d0b19093d330149390ac9","tid":948841,"uid":99700,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T11:10:15.000Z","msg":"搵"},{"pid":"aa0abca11017a386f1d9af986c8e754ac7e40947","tid":948841,"uid":16612,"like":44,"dislike":2,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T11:10:59.000Z","msg":"agger<br />\nbtw 穩你老母"},{"pid":"e30d422755de4a7ed4f35e5c876159592d9fbfa1","tid":948841,"uid":51121,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T11:11:30.000Z","msg":"呢度都無咩道理講"},{"pid":"799cae35148a4a9e342c93e80dd7fc1eec6fcbb9","tid":948841,"uid":213877,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T11:11:38.000Z","msg":"咁叫穩錢？屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n小學未畢業就搵你老豆啦<br />\n<br />\n戇鳩仔"},{"pid":"7c3f0544f39c2e90c0e197496bd4aa309cdb6be4","tid":948841,"uid":74702,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"aa0abca11017a386f1d9af986c8e754ac7e40947","tid":948841,"uid":16612,"like":44,"dislike":2,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T11:10:59.000Z","msg":"agger<br />\nbtw 穩你老母"